	7. ``The Thomas Crown Affair,'' MGM, $2.7 million, 1,849  
locations, $1,460 average, $61.3 million, six weeks. 
</P>
<P>
	8. ``Mickey Blue Eyes,'' Warner Bros., $2.2 million, 1,975  
locations, $1,120 average, $30.3 million, four weeks. 
</P>
