	9. ``Chill Factor,'' Warner Bros., $1.9 million, 2,558  
locations, $758 average, $9.6 million, two weeks. 
</P>
<P>
	10. ``The Blair Witch Project,'' Artisan, $1.6 million, 1,937  
locations, $842 average, $136.2 million, nine weeks. 
</P>
<P>
	11. ``Love Stinks,'' Independent Artists, $1.3 million, 1,325  
locations, $1,011 average, $1.3 million, one week. 
</P>
<P>
	12. ``In Too Deep,'' Dimension, $1.2 million, 641 locations,  
$1,933 average, $11.9 million, three weeks. 
</P>
