(130) this year. Showalter said he did not know when the third 
baseman would return. 
</P>
<P>
	``He's gone for as long as it takes him to feel comfortable  
about the situation,'' Showalter said. 
</P>
<P>
	Lenny Harris, acquired from the Colorado Rockies for minor  
league infielder Belvani Martinez on Aug. 31, started Tuesday night 
against the Pirates. 
  	   	
